<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Aura Events - Welcome</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #000;
            color: #eee;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #111;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.2);
        }

        .brand {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ffc107;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 1rem;
            animation: fadeInDown 1s ease-out forwards;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.3rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ffc107;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            color: #ddd;
        }

        .main-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 2rem;
            padding: 2rem;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: #222;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            width: 400px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }

        .card h2 {
            color: #ffc107;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .card p {
            color: #ddd;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .btn {
            background-color: #ffc107;
            color: #000;
            border: none;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #fff;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1rem;
            background-color: #111;
            color: #ffc107;
            margin-top: auto;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInDown {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <a href="#" class="brand">
            <i class="fas fa-crown"></i> Aura Events
        </a>
    </nav>

    <div class="hero">
        <h1>Welcome to Aura Events</h1>
        <p>Your Ultimate Event Planning & Business Platform</p>
    </div>

    <div class="main-container">
        <div class="card">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i> Plan Your Event</h2>
            <p>Looking to create memorable moments? Find everything you need for your special occasions - from venues and photographers to catering and decor. Book trusted professionals and premium services all in one place.</p>
            <button class="btn" onclick="window.location.href='user'">Book Services</button>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-store"></i> List Your Services</h2>
            <p>Are you a service provider? Join our platform to showcase your expertise and grow your business. Connect with clients planning weddings, anniversaries, corporate events, and more. Register your services today.</p>
            <button class="btn" onclick="window.location.href='admin'">Register Business</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2025 Aura Events. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>